------BASIC ROUTER CONFIG--------------
service nagle (Congestion control algorithm, that help process the tcp session to the router)
no service pad (not used anymore)
service tcp-keepalives-in (sends keep alive for remote tcp) 
service tcp-keepalives-out 
!
service timestamps debug datetime msec localtime show-timezone
service timestamps log datetime msec localtime show-timezone
service password-encryption
service internal
service disable-ip-fast-frag
service sequence-numbers
!
hostname PE2
!
logging buffered 32768
logging buffered debugging
no logging console
no logging monitor
enable secret cisco
!
clock timezone PST -8 0
clock summer-time PDT recurring
!
ip cef
!
no ip domain lookup
ip domain name mylab.com
!
username admin privilege 15 secret cisco
!
ip tcp synwait-time 5
ip ssh authentication-retries 5
ip ssh version 2
no ip http server
no ip http secure-server
!
no cdp run
!
banner exec ^
2 - Lab Provider Edge Router (Data Center 2)
^
!
line con 0
password cisco
logging synchronous
login local
transport preferred ssh
transport output ssh
stopbits 1

line vty 0 4
password cisco
logging synchronous
login local
transport preferred ssh
transport input ssh
transport output ssh

line vty 5 15
login
transport preferred none
transport input none
transport output none
end

crypto key gen rsa general-keys modulus 1024

---------------------END---------------------------
